1. *Jer* svi znamo da je to istina. (Because we all know that this is true.)
2. *Jer* smo mi svi jedno. (Because we are all one.)
3. Bez obzira na to *jer* je to jedini izlaz. (No matter, because it is the only way out.)
4. Oni su to mogli da urade samo *jer* su bili spremni da se izlože riziku. (They could only do it because they were willing to take the risk.)
5. Ja sam se odlučio za to *jer* sam znao da je to ispravan pristup. (I chose to do it because I knew it was the right approach.)